{'id': 2022609, 'body': "Hello, you're right about Velocity and motorcycles with BPme. 

While you cannot use your Velocity card via our BPme app, you can continue to use your Velocity Frequent Flyer card in-store.

With respect to motorcycles - rules about mobile phone usage outside your vehicle have not changed and remain unacceptable. You can, however, safely use your phone (and BPme) from the comfort of inside your stationary vehicle. Given the nature of a motorcycle, they do not comply with this rule. Please do contact aucustcare@bp.com if you have any further questions on this.", 'modified': '2017-12-14T00:03:54Z'}

