{'id': 3216245, 'body': 'Hi there, we appreciate that you share our concern for data security. 

We have introduced the fuel payment function to help customers save time. BPme is transformational and we are planning a whole range of exciting new offers to make our customers lives easier. You can continue to use your Velocity Frequent Flyer card in-store to earn and redeem points on fuel and retail purchases at BP. Watch this space for new BPme features in the future. 

Unfortunately Velocity Frequent Flyer isn’t able to award points retrospectively if you have used the app to accumulate points.', 'modified': '2018-04-23T00:44:11Z'}

